data.description: Your country dream home is now a reality! Grab your slice of Porum while you still can! This beautifully updated 4 bedroom home sits on a gorgeous 1 acre lot with mature trees and plenty of room to roam! This home features a large kitchen with tons of custom cabinetry and ample counter space. Beautiful vaulted ceiling in the main living area that highlights the stunning brick fireplace with pellet stove insert! Bedrooms are all great sized, there is a second living area that has a door in which you could use as a 5th bedroom! This could be the perfect home for you! Enjoy life away from the hustle and bustle of big city living! This home is just 5 minutes south of I-40 at the Highway 2 turn off. Living in the country doesn't mean being far from convenience, in fact you can enjoy eating delicious Mexican cuisine at El Jarocho Mexican Restaurant just 5 minutes north in Warner. Schedule a showing of this beautiful home today.
